{"tid":696762,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"（Bass撚）新手問題","createTime":"2018-06-10T11:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T09:34:20.000Z","uid":77600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"a8ac1e52aef3a4e0d3c396c06b9c1b48babf0182","tid":696762,"uid":77600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:27:47.000Z","msg":"想問下初學除左爬音階仲有乜好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日一拎上手就無腦咁爬格仔 得閒會就記下啲音<br />\n想練下歌但又唔識睇譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求巴打講下點學先快上手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自學左5日"},{"pid":"10cc6b1f1f5b54afca04f1fff40d0668cdafb821","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"自學3日 留名推post<br />\n乜都冇睇就買左枝bass<br />\n買左枝5 線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點上手好"},{"pid":"c3e2f8e7ec0925a3ae677d0dd4c94c47217700b1","tid":696762,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10cc6b1f1f5b54afca04f1fff40d0668cdafb821","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"自學3日 留名推post<br />\n乜都冇睇就買左枝bass<br />\n買左枝5 線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點上手好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"點解唔買4線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f440f677dee96f0a21721e30ddfccdd8190306ac","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"c3e2f8e7ec0925a3ae677d0dd4c94c47217700b1","tid":696762,"uid":53736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10cc6b1f1f5b54afca04f1fff40d0668cdafb821","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"d