-10T11:42:29.000Z","msg":"加油 話唔定好事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e624e77f8fe00d7325cec3f3c694ba48556bc60","tid":696762,"uid":139016,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T11:46:32.000Z","msg":"學樂理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n悲時佬要有好樂理底先會勁<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">其實樣樣野都要好樂理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"82103ac6bf44c1d337a87e950acffa7dd8e41bb0","tid":696762,"uid":180018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"4線tab譜識唔識睇？（雖然你個case係5線）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住啲1234照彈返第幾條線第幾格，搵隻鍾意嘅歌慢慢彈。<br />\n<br />\n唔彈歌好易悶然後放棄。"},{"pid":"f584e34f53aea81a2737f4e75d2e07823343c005","tid":696762,"uid":77600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82103ac6bf44c1d337a87e950acffa7dd8e41bb0","tid":696762,"uid":180018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:04:43.000Z","msg":"4線tab譜識唔識睇？（雖然你個case係5線）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n跟住啲1234照彈返第幾條線第幾格，搵隻鍾意嘅歌慢慢彈。<br />\n<br />\n唔彈歌好易悶然後放棄。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:12:48.000Z","msg":"而家就係  無歌彈<br />\n日日爬格仔好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f4b873365aeafc6bd189972359d7349e5cf1f68","tid":696762,"uid":36817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"d格距咁遠其實都有排爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1534f6d77b33d26ee826471bc8c2400a060d5cd8","tid":696762,"uid":77600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6f4b873365aeafc6bd189972359d7349e5cf1f68","tid":696762,"uid":36817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T12:14:10.000Z","msg":"d格距咁遠其實都有排爬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"但真係好悶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710f7838f80feabfdf425174eda78417269987dc","tid":696762,"uid":60451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"彈scales <br />\nMajor同 minor<br />\n都有排練<br />\nBpm 70~120 8分音<br />\n跟著可以試下16分音"},{"pid":"44b151df3f25814b393663f96b2755b27840f4df","tid":696762,"uid":60451,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:50:06.000Z","msg":"通常睇譜都係數字譜多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/001035_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F001035_f7f0bbdb094d0b83d7561fc5ec2130d7.PNG&h=44b78b13&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以4線Bass為例<br />\nE線係最低音嘅線<br />\nG線係最高音嘅線<br />\n依個圖中所彈嘅係Gmajor scales<br />\n以依個係pattern放返去其他音就會係其他音嘅major scales.<br />\n例如:<br />\nCmajor scales<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/001957_ed15309095e612491ee3f1f7bd27241b.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F001957_ed15309095e612491ee3f1f7bd27241b.PNG&h=7081fcd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n通常彈Scales都會有特定手形<br />\n咁我簡單講下最普遍嗰個先<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/003236_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F003236_10fb15c77258a991b0028080a64fb42d.png&h=a939b8c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以數字代表手指<br />\n1:食指<br />\n2:中指<br />\n3:無名指<br />\n4:尾指<br />\n以依個pattern去彈就會fit返手形<br />\n會彈得幾舒服<br />\n<br />\n5線個譜都係一樣<br />\n依個係Dmajor Scales<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/004340_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F004340_7f3d58b193ac4ce8e0730da9d0d6e8ce.PNG&h=a484a6c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果見到譜冇第5條線就唔彈5條線都OK.<br />\n咁當然想彈都無所謂啦只要啱音就OK<br />\n<br />\n希望對自學新手有D用啦"},{"pid":"f0412e39363b1eb53e0cfb2241c8ab3ec5fdc463","tid":696762,"uid":60451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T16:52:09.000Z","msg":"唔記得左講返上邊D譜嘅數字係格仔.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由Bass最頭個位開始數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94c5f7418512fff60f10c043943bd3a7c2781e3c","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"想問右手tech <br />\n係咪一般都淨用食指同中指？<br />\n點決定幾時用食指幾時用中指？"},{"pid":"3a131cfd956f236fa503d0d5cf9d7676e74c8037","tid":696762,"uid":60451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94c5f7418512fff60f10c043943bd3a7c2781e3c","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"想問右手tech <br />\n係咪一般都淨用食指同中指？<br />\n點決定幾時用食指幾時用中指？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"仲會用母指同無名指<br />\nSlap用母指<br />\n無名指係彈D好快嘅野時會有機會用到<br />\n或者tapping都會用無名指<br />\n<br />\n咁幾時用食指定中指<br />\n普遍都會第一個彈嘅音會用食指<br />\n我指個由冇彈任何音之後彈嘅第一粒音<br />\n係過線嘅時候就會有D特別<br />\n<br />\n普遍都係下圖咁彈<br />\n由低音線到高音線<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/011848_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F011848_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png&h=a3131ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1:右手食指<br />\n2:右手中指<br />\n係上一條線嘅第一粒音就用另一隻手指<br />\n<br />\n咁由高音線去低音線<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/013028_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F013028_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=345d9ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1:右手食指<br />\n2:右手中指<br />\n係高音線落返低一條線嘅第一粒音就會用返同一隻手指落<br />\n<br />\n誇左線就會好似咁彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/014002_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F014002_9eb9cd58b9ea5e04c890326b5c1f471f.png&h=0e572cd1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6a96c37151002e4ff1d9ce978bb332c81ea3b40","tid":696762,"uid":77600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a131cfd956f236fa503d0d5cf9d7676e74c8037","tid":696762,"uid":60451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94c5f7418512fff60f10c043943bd3a7c2781e3c","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"想問右手tech <br />\n係咪一般都淨用食指同中指？<br />\n點決定幾時用食指幾時用中指？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-10T17:40:38.000Z","msg":"仲會用母指同無名指<br />\nSlap用母指<br />\n無名指係彈D好快嘅野時會有機會用到<br />\n或者tapping都會用無名指<br />\n<br />\n咁幾時用食指定中指<br />\n普遍都會第一個彈嘅音會用食指<br />\n我指個由冇彈任何音之後彈嘅第一粒音<br />\n係過線嘅時候就會有D特別<br />\n<br />\n普遍都係下圖咁彈<br />\n由低音線到高音線<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/011848_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F011848_8266e4bfeda1bd42d8f9794eb4ea0a13.png&h=a3131ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1:右手食指<br />\n2:右手中指<br />\n係上一條線嘅第一粒音就用另一隻手指<br />\n<br />\n咁由高音線去低音線<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/013028_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F11%2F013028_f19c9085129709ee14d013be869df69b.png&h=345d9ad5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1:右手食指<br />\n2:右手中指<br />\n係高音線落返低一條線嘅第一粒音就會用返同一隻手指落<br />\n<br />\n誇左線就會好似咁彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/11/014002_9eb9cd58b9ea5