,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T10:51:51.000Z","msg":"我自己就上網學手勢 之後買書學樂理同增進技巧"},{"pid":"9a3e3fb347e74d1b7e0c133bf02f6c5ebe114fd7","tid":696762,"uid":90499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1c8df3448b483e46e18bfd286e1f17b7e052adc","tid":696762,"uid":60451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"27d132b349d6bcc0d9fab4f28f6802331e5b7057","tid":696762,"uid":62532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b1ead92741061d2009c06e6e38318a2c0d1f244","tid":696762,"uid":60451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:12:19.000Z","msg":"一段句子嘅第一個bar開頭<br />\n就由食指開頭 如果中間有休止符或者廷長線又或者係8分音去16分音就唔一定要變返食指開始<br />\n<br />\n例如你講嘅16分licks<br />\n1  na2 na3 na4 na <br />\n1  212 121  212  12<br />\n<br />\n其實好睇順唔順手<br />\n好多人都覺得順手彈到就算<br />\n所以有好多唔同派系"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問多個右手tech問題 <br />\n網上教右手要用姆指mute彈緊既對上一條線<br />\n我想問既情況係例如：<br />\nG-----5-------<br />\nD--5----7-5--<br />\nA---------------<br />\nE---------------<br />\n以上為一個16 分音符既1ena<br />\n我應該為左G線果一粒音特登將姆指移低一條線mute條D線嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  多謝指教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T01:39:10.000Z","msg":"我就建議唔落<br />\n繼續留係A線<br />\n<br />\n右手tech派系好多<br />\n我最近學緊姆指只禁pickup<br />\n完全同我初學唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:15:35.000Z","msg":"我就係放係pickup，彈幼線好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bb972a1a202a547f3c20c8a2a034666f7b465e","tid":696762,"uid":74304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0125c2b2b99112db8dd2e6fada24e6e40a5fec8d","tid":696762,"uid":77600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"